                    <p id="req-uppercase" class="requirement-text">❌ At least one upper case letter</p>
                    <p id="req-number" class="requirement-text">❌ At least one numeral (0–9)</p>
                    <p id="req-symbol" class="requirement-text">❌ At least one symbol (!#^*_- etc.)</p>
